==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tow-head
<hw>Tow"-head`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>An
urchin who has soft, whitish hair.</def> <mark>[Colloq.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>The hooded merganser.</def>
<mark>[ Local, U. S. ]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>A low alluvial island or shoal in a river.</def>
<mark>[Local, U. S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Towhee</ent>⟦br⟧
